---
title: Pork & Poblano Tacos All In One Pan
description: Shake up taco night with an unexpected topping: kiwi salsa! The fruit is a surprisingly good fit next to south-of-the-border flavors, bringing sweetness and tanginess that matches the ground pork seasoned with our Mexican spice blend. It’s balanced out by a cool lime crema and tender pieces of poblano pepper, coming together in a taste adventure unlike anything else you’ve ever experienced in a tortilla.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-and-poblano-tacos-f6863970.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/pork-and-poblano-tacos-5e7a445c54d97b7a06299aa2-a4ef73ef.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Mexican
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/pork-and-poblano-tacos-5e7a445c54d97b7a06299aa2
nutrition:
  calories: 900 kcal
  fat: 48 g
  saturated fat: 17 g
